lso affirm the age-metallicity\nrelation, predicted by an earlier model, in which metal-rich clusters are\nsystematically several billion years younger than their metal-poor\ncounterparts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 May 2014 01:39:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Nov 2014 22:04:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
